engine. Check out this quick preview video for an overview of &#8230; <a href=\"http://tri.be/easy-digital-downloads-tickets-a-preview/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;</span></a>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3:\"Rob\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1353:\"<p>As you might have <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ModernTribeInc/status/394923614635454464\">seen us tease</a> earlier this week on Twitter, we&#8217;ve been working on a whirlwind of a project with our friend <a href=\"https://twitter.com/pippinsplugins\">Pippin Williamson</a> recently. Today we&#8217;re stoked to finally show you the fruits of those labors: <strong>EDD Tickets</strong>, a new add-on for <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/the-events-calendar/\">The Events Calendar</a> and <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/plugins/easy-digital-downloads/\">Easy Digital Downloads</a> that allows you to sell event tickets using EDD as your commerce engine.</p>\n<p>Check out this quick preview video for an overview of the setup and use:</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"//player.vimeo.com/video/78122977\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>We&#8217;re still ironing out a few of the features, including a nifty option to download your ticket directly from the purchase confirmation page, which will be included in the final release. As for a timeline &#8212; that&#8217;ll depend on what we dig up in the QA process this week. We&#8217;re optimistic based on what we&#8217;ve seen so far and hope to have this available for download sometime in the coming weeks. Stay tuned!</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"http://tri.be/easy-digital-downloads-tickets-a-preview/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"Free Plugins For Non-Profits!\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26:\"http://tri.be/non-profits/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:35:\"http://tri.be/non-profits/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 22 Oct 2013 15:39:16 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"Products\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"http://tri.be/?p=72036\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:522:\"Are you a non-profit organization in the market for one of our plugins? Well I&#8217;ve got some good news then: you can have all of them…for free! That&#8217;s right, FREE. You might be wondering why? It is simple. You help people. We like like to help people. If you do a better job organizing and serving your community by using our events platform, then the world gets just a little bit better every time. Events &#8230; <a href=\"http://tri.be/non-profits/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;</span></a>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"cambrennan\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2662:\"<p>Are you a non-profit organization in the market for one of our <a href=\"http://tri.be/products/\">plugins</a>? Well I&#8217;ve got some good news then: you can have all of them…for free!</p>\n<p>That&#8217;s right, FREE.</p>\n<p>You might be wondering why? It is simple. You help people. We like like to help people. If you do a better job organizing and serving your community by using our events platform, then the world gets just a little bit better every time.</p>\n<h2>Events Calendar PRO Makes the World Better</h2>\n<p>Here are some non-profit organizations that have already taken advantage of this free hookup:</p>\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.womenrockinc.org/\">Women Rock Inc</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://tri.be/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Events_for_October_2013___Women_Rock__Inc..jpg\"></a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"http://newyork.thecityatlas.org/events/\">Artist As Citizen</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://tri.be/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Mad._Sq._Eats.jpg\"></a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.jazzschool.org\">Jazzschool</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://tri.be/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/»_Jazzschool.jpg\"></a></p>\n<p>These are just a few examples of the many non-profit organizations that have taken advantage of this opportunity. In fact, we&#8217;ve donated over $2,500 in staff hours in order to make sure that our non-profit friends are taken care of in an excellent manner.</p>\n<h2>Hook Me Up With a Free Copy of Events Calendar PRO for WordPress!</h2>\n<p>So if you are a non-profit organization and are interested in getting ahold of our plugins, here is what you need to do:</p>\n<p>email us at pro [at] tri.be with the following information:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Your organization name and url</li>\n<li>The name and email of the contact person for your organization, in case we need to get in touch</li>\n<li>Proof of your organization’s 501(c)3 status or your country’s equivalent</li>\n</ul>\n<p>After we receive the necessary information we&#8217;ll send you a .zip file of the plugins you request! All we ask is that you link back to the Modern Tribe site on your calendar or sponsor page, and do a thank you post on Facebook and/or Twitter.</p>\n<p>If you would like access to updates, our support team and the forums you will have to purchase a full license, as support + updates are <strong>not</strong> included in the free non-profit program. We have also chosen not to provide free licenses to non-profit organizations that are primarily religious or political due to the diverse nature of the beliefs and convictions represented on our team.</p>\n<p>Remember, email us at pro [at] tri.be if you are interested, we&#8217;d love to help out your organization!</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"http://tri.be/non-profits/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_ba