 to see how factors interact. This view can help trace root causes and suggest innovative policy solutions. Here is one representation of a food system, from Agricultural Urbanism: HB Lanarc publishers.\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Growing, Processing, Transportation &amp; Storage, Distribution,  Eating &amp; Celebrating, Waste Recovery and Education all interact to create a food system\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Agricultural-Urbanism.png\" />\r\n<h2>Members</h2>\r\nMembers of FPCSA are drawn from diverse sectors of the food system. Membership slots are limited, and applications are received only for open sectors. Volunteering with a standing committee, a working group, or events is a good way to get acquainted with the organization to decide whether to apply for a slot you might qualify for. It’s also a way for us to get to know you, your interests and your strengths.\r\n\r\nBoard\r\n<h2>Meetings</h2>','About','','inherit','closed','open','','8-revision-v1','','','2013-12-05 13:21:20','2013-12-05 19:21:20','',8,'/26',0,'revision','',0),(27,3,'2013-12-05 13:27:23','2013-12-05 19:27:23','<h2>Volunteer</h2>\r\n<h3>Events</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Staffing tables at farmers markets and community health fairs</li>\r\n<li>Community outreach meetings</li>\r\n<li>Conferences</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Workgroups and committees</h3>\r\n<li>Standing committees include Communications, Research and Measures, Development, and Membership</li>\r\n<li>Workgroups are organized around current issues. You can propose one if you are willing to take a leadership role in it. Current issues include:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>researching downtown grocery needs, market conditions and business models</li>\r\n<li>urban agriculture policies</li>\r\n<li>Unified Development Code revisions</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Donate</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>[sdonations]1[/sdonations] Your donations help pay for our events and community outreach. We have benefitted from the work of unpaid interns in the past, and we would like to offer stipends for future interns.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Applying for membership</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Applications are open for certain sectors of the food system (see the <a href=\"/about\">About page</a>). Membership is like a board position, and carries obligations of time for meeting preparation and follow-up, additional participation in a standing committee, and communication to and from your constituents. Applicants are rigorously screened for experience in their fields and leadership ability. Volunteering on a standing committee or workgroup can be a good way to learn more about the council and whether membership obligations would be a good fit for you.</p> \r\n\r\n<p>Current openings are in:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Agriculture-Government Agency</li>\r\n	<li>Agriculture Education</li>\r\n	<li>Community Organizing</li>\r\n	<li>Concerned Citizen</li>\r\n	<li>Consumption (Restaurant)</li>\r\n	<li>Education-K-12</li>\r\n	<li>Education-University (Research)</li>\r\n	<li>Government - City Council or Staff</li>\r\n	<li>Government - Mayor\'s Office</li>\r\n	<li>Health-Institutions</li>\r\n	<li>Planning/Policy</li>\r\n	<li>Processing</li>\r\n	<li>Retail-Farmers Market</li>\r\n	<li>Retail-Grocery</li>\r\n	<li>Waste Recovery</li>\r\n	<li>Water </li>\r\n</ul>','Get Involved','','publish','closed','closed','','get-involved','','','2013-12-07 09:46:17','2013-12-07 15:46:17','',0,'/?page_id=27',0,'page','',0),(28,2,'2013-12-05 13:27:16','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','closed','open','','','','','2013-12-05 13:27:16','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'/?p=28',0,'post','',0),(29,3,'2013-12-05 13:27:23','2013-12-05 19:27:23','<h2>Volunteer</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2>Donate</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2>Our Supporters</h2>\r\n','Get Involved','','inherit','closed','open','','27-revision-v1','','','2013-12-05 13:27:23','2013-12-05 19:27:23','',27,'/29',0,'revision','',0),(30,2,'2013-12-05 13:27:55','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','closed','open','','','','','2013-12-05 13:27:5